column2: select a.*,DayNumber=DATEDIFF(day,&&&,a.date)+# as day   from (select top # _id,ATS_SYSTEM_CODE,location.ToString() as location      from schoollocation sl where fiscal_year=#) l      join schoolattendance a       on a.school=l.ATS_SYSTEM_CODE        and a.date between &&& and &&&        order by date
